ne by the customer. Cancellation and Refund When the customer places the order, at Easy Move we start the preparation for the transport and make a commitment with the carrier that will carry out the transport, which in turn reserves a van and a driver for the transport. Any cancellation of this commitment incurs costs for the carrier and automatically transfers these costs to Easy Move, so the customer can cancel but the amount of the refund will depend on when the cancellation is made. Cancellation up to 48 hours before the collection date - 10% fee on the amount paid. Cancellation less than 48 hours before collection - 30% fee on the amount paid.\')}} After collection of the cargo, no refund is possible. Help to Load/Unload The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work. About Insurance Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance. Types of vans and measurements The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will alwa