(767, 'es', 'About US Easy Move Europe is an online digital platform that connects companies and private persons to a huge van network, simplifying and making relocation of business and personal assets affordable, through an algorithm that offers prices instantly, with transparency. The company was founded with the goal of providing an efficient and reliable transportation service for businesses and individuals in Europe. We are headquartered in Bucharest, RO, and our team of experienced drivers and logistic experts will ensure that your shipment arrives at its destination, safely, securely, and on time. \"Everything becomes obvious once you know the answer\" James Kaljes (Owner)', 'Acerca de EE.UU. Easy Move Europe es una plataforma digital online que conecta a empresas y particulares a una enorme red de furgonetas, simplificando y haciendo asequible la reubicacin de activos empresariales y personales, a travs de un algoritmo que ofrece precios al instante y con transparencia. La empresa se fund con el objetivo de proporcionar un servicio de transporte eficiente y fiable para empresas y particulares en Europa. Nuestra sede est en Bucarest, RO, y nuestro equipo de conductores experimentados y expertos en logstica se asegurar de que su envo llegue a su destino de forma segura y puntual. &quot;Todo se vuelve obvio una vez que sabes la respuesta&quot; James Kaljes (Propietario)', '2023-08-25 00:29:10', '2023-08-25 00:29:10'),
