(880, 'es', 'The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work.', 'El conductor no est obligado a ayudar a cargar o descargar la carga. Si el cliente necesita asistencia, deber contratarla directamente con Easy Move. Se prestar asistencia de carga y/o descarga desde la planta baja a la furgoneta y desde la furgoneta a la planta baja, para artculos con un peso no superior a 20 kilos. Durante todo el proceso, el cliente deber ayudar o contratar a terceros para que le ayuden sin excepcin. Para recibir ayuda para cargar o descargar en/desde los apartamentos, el cliente debe avisar con antelacin y est sujeto a aprobacin, ya que no todos los conductores pueden hacer esfuerzo fsico y el equipo de Easy Move debe elegir al conductor con antelacin para que pueda realizar dicho trabajo. .', '2023-08-25 00:37:26', '2023-08-25 00:37:26'),
(881, 'es', 'Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance.', 'Cada envo realizado con nuestra entrega exclusiva en camioneta est cubierto por las convenciones CMR y tambin est disponible la responsabilidad extendida (para envos comerciales). El valor ronda actualmente los 10 euros el kilo y se aplica en caso de robo, mercanca daada y negligencia grave en el transporte nacional e internacional. Tenga en cuenta que cualquier dao a la carga causado por negligencia en el embalaje de la carga, como lo demuestran fotos o videos, est sujeto a la prdida del derecho a pagar el seguro.', '2023-08-25 00:37:26', '2023-08-25 00:37:26'),
(882, 'es', 'The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that the client provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van.', 'El tamao en la descripcin es un promedio, los tamaos pueden variar. Siempre intentaremos mantener la capacidad contratada por usted (13 y 19 metros cbicos), por lo que es importante que el cliente nos facilite la mayor informacin posible sobre su carga para que podamos enviarle la furgoneta adecuada.', '2023-08-25 00:37:26', '2023-08-25 00:37:26'),
(883, 'es', 'Easy Move is committed to treating all data in accordance with international data protection laws, based on the following principles: - Purpose limitation. - Data minimisation. - Accuracy. - Storage limitation. - Integrity and confidentiality (security) - Accountability.', 'Easy Move se compromete a tratar todos los datos de conformidad con las leyes internacionales de proteccin de datos, basndose en los siguientes principios: - Limitacin de la finalidad. - Minimizacin de datos. - Exactitud. - Limitacin de almacenamiento. - Integridad y confidencialidad (seguridad) - Responsabilidad.', '2023-08-25 00:37:26', '2023-08-25 00:37:26'),
(884, 'es', 'Any doubts or requests for data deletion can be requested from the Easy Move team at any time.Lawfulness, fairness and transparency. For any question, please contact us: info@easymoveeurope.com', 'Cualquier duda o solicitud de supresin de datos se puede solicitar al equipo de Easy Move en cualquier momento. Legalidad, equidad y transparencia. Para cualquier pregunta, por favor contctenos: info@easymoveeurope.com', '2023-08-25 00:37:27', '2023-08-25 00:37:27'),
(885, 'es', 'How it works Contact About US My account Open Account Log In English Deutsch Italian French Espaol Portugal Polish Romanian Privacy and Condition Terms and Conditions Our terms and conditions are not intended to hide information or take advantage of any situation. We only aim to be fair to all parties involved. Firstly with the customer who is paying for a quality service to be done, secondly, be fair with our partners, carriers and drivers who have transportation as a means of livelihood and with our team that aims to make a profit, but without harming anyone, very on the contrary. General terms When booking the Van delivery service, the customer agrees for the shipment to be available,properly packed and secured for transportation at the pick-up address for the carrier to collect it from 8:00 to 18:00 or another hours agreed previous with Easy Move team. The selected carrier will contact the customer upon its arrival at the pick-up address. On a rare occasion, due to unforeseen factors related to the selected carrier, pick-up can be performed before or after the scheduled date. If the van/driver of the selected carrier will not show up on the scheduled pick-up date or is not providing the services like help to load/unload, the customer assumes the responsibility of informing Easy Move immediately about this fact, so that Easy Move can check the situation with the carrier and fix the issue as soon as possible. The customer is always able to get information about the transit of the shipment by contacting Easy Move support team, which will check the latest transit updates directly with the carrier. The customer shall be informed about the estimated time of delivery in advance. If the consignee is not available at the delivery address, the driver will wait at the address until the customer can organize the unloading of the shipment, as agreed. The customer is aware that any unnecessary waiting by the driver may result in additional costs that shall be borne by the customer. Cancellation and Refund When the customer places the order, at Easy Move we start the preparation for the transport and make a commitment with the carrier that will carry out the transport, which in turn reserves a van and a driver for the transport. Any cancellation of this commitment incurs costs for the carrier and automatically transfers these costs to Easy Move, so the customer can cancel but the amount of the refund will depend on when the cancellation is made. Cancellation up to 48 hours before the collection date - 10% fee on the amount paid. Cancellation less than 48 hours before collection - 30% fee on the amount paid.\')}} After collection of the cargo, no refund is possible. Help to Load/Unload The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work. About Insurance Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance. Types of vans and measurements The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will alwa