(925, 'pt', 'Customized pick-up and delivery time- Collection and deliveries on weekends, day and night -Same day collection available for urgent transport Transport of heavy and bulky items -No special packaging is required -Ideal for transporting fragile items', 'Horrios de recolha e entrega personalizados - Recolha e entrega aos fins-de-semana, dia e noite - Recolha no prprio dia disponvel para transporte urgente Transporte de artigos pesados e volumosos - No necessita de embalagem especial - Ideal para o transporte de artigos frgeis', '2023-08-25 00:38:57', '2023-08-25 00:38:57'),
(926, 'pt', 'With our friends of Easy move, we can put our cargo in their hands and focus on our business, as they are reliable and extremely professional.With them, we don\'t have dissatisfied customers calling us asking where the cargo is or complaining about delays.', 'Com nossos amigos da Easy move podemos colocar nossa carga nas mos deles e focar no nosso negcio, pois so confiveis e extremamente profissionais. Com eles, no temos clientes insatisfeitos nos ligando perguntando onde est a carga ou reclamando atrasos.', '2023-08-25 00:38:57', '2023-08-25 00:38:57'),
(927, 'pt', 'We have already used Easy Move Europe\'s services 2 times for relocation and each time they have been extremely efficient And always go above and beyond expectations. I have already recommended it to several friends and they are all satisfied.', 'J utilizmos 2 vezes os servios da Easy Move Europe para relocalizao e sempre foram extremamente eficientes e sempre superam as expectativas. J recomendei a vrios amigos e todos ficaram satisfeitos.', '2023-08-25 00:38:57', '2023-08-25 00:38:57'),
(928, 'pt', 'Easy Move Europe is an online digital platform that connects companies and private persons to a huge van network, simplifying and making relocation of business and personal assets affordable, through an algorithm that offers prices instantly, with transparency.', 'Easy Move Europe  uma plataforma digital online que liga empresas e particulares a uma enorme rede de carrinhas, simplificando e tornando acessvel a relocalizao de bens empresariais e pessoais, atravs de um algoritmo que oferece preos instantaneamente, com transparncia.', '2023-08-25 00:38:57', '2023-08-25 00:38:57'),
(929, 'pt', 'The company was founded with the goal of providing an efficient and reliable transportation service for businesses and individuals in Europe. We are headquartered in Bucharest, RO, and our team of experienced drivers and logistic experts will ensure that your shipment arrives at its destination, safely, securely, and on time.', 'A empresa foi fundada com o objetivo de fornecer um servio de transporte eficiente e confivel para empresas e indivduos na Europa. Estamos sediados em Bucareste, RO, e nossa equipe de motoristas experientes e especialistas em logstica garantir que sua remessa chegue ao destino com segurana e dentro do prazo.', '2023-08-25 00:38:57', '2023-08-25 00:42:26'),
