(1120, 'pt', 'The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work.', 'O motorista no  obrigado a ajudar a carregar ou descarregar a carga. Caso o cliente necessite de assistncia, esta dever ser contratada diretamente com a Easy Move. Ser prestada assistncia de carga e/ou descarga do trreo at a van e da van at o trreo, para itens com peso no superior a 20 quilos. Durante todo o processo, o cliente dever ajudar ou contratar terceiros para ajudar, sem exceo. Para ajuda na carga ou descarga nos/dos apartamentos, o cliente necessita de avisar com antecedncia e est sujeito a aprovao, pois nem todos os motoristas podem realizar esforo fsico e a equipa da Easy Move necessita de escolher previamente o motorista para que este possa realizar tal trabalho. .', '2023-08-25 00:46:20', '2023-08-25 00:46:20'),
(1121, 'pt', 'Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance.', 'Cada remessa com nossa entrega em van dedicada  coberta pelas convenes CMR e a responsabilidade estendida tambm est disponvel (para remessas comerciais). O valor ronda atualmente os 10 euros por quilo e aplica-se  ocorrncia de furto, bens danificados, negligncia grave em transportes internacionais e nacionais. Observe que qualquer dano  carga causado por negligncia no acondicionamento da carga, conforme comprovado por fotos ou vdeos, est sujeito  perda do direito ao pagamento do seguro.', '2023-08-25 00:46:20', '2023-08-25 00:46:20'),
(1122, 'pt', 'The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that the client provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van.', 'O tamanho na descrio  uma mdia, os tamanhos podem variar. Tentaremos sempre manter a capacidade contratada por voc (13 e 19 metros cbicos), por isso  importante que o cliente nos fornea o mximo de informaes possvel sobre sua carga para que possamos lhe enviar a van adequada.', '2023-08-25 00:46:20', '2023-08-25 00:46:20'),
(1123, 'pt', 'Easy Move is committed to treating all data in accordance with international data protection laws, based on the following principles: - Purpose limitation. - Data minimisation. - Accuracy. - Storage limitation. - Integrity and confidentiality (security) - Accountability.', 'A Easy Move assume o compromisso de tratar todos os dados de acordo com as leis internacionais de proteo de dados, com base nos seguintes princpios: - Limitao da finalidade. - Minimizao de dados. - Preciso. - Limitao de armazenamento. - Integridade e confidencialidade (segurana) - Responsabilidade.', '2023-08-25 00:46:20', '2023-08-25 00:46:20'),
(1124, 'pt', 'Any doubts or requests for data deletion can be requested from the Easy Move team at any time.Lawfulness, fairness and transparency. For any question, please contact us: info@easymoveeurope.com', 'Qualquer dvida ou pedido de eliminao de dados pode ser solicitado a qualquer momento  equipa da Easy Move. Legalidade, equidade e transparncia. Para qualquer questo, por favor contacte-nos: info@easymoveeurope.com', '2023-08-25 00:46:20', '2023-08-25 00:46:20'),
(1125, 'pt', 'How it works Contact About US My account Open Account Log In English Deutsch Italian French Espaol Portugal Polish Romanian Privacy and Condition Terms and Conditions Our terms and conditions are not intended to hide information or take advantage of any situation. We only aim to be fair to all parties involved. Firstly with the customer who is paying for a quality service to be done, secondly, be fair with our partners, carriers and drivers who have transportation as a means of livelihood and with our team that aims to make a profit, but without harming anyone, very on the contrary. General terms When booking the Van delivery service, the customer agrees for the shipment to be available,properly packed and secured for transportation at the pick-up address for the carrier to collect it from 8:00 to 18:00 or another hours agreed previous with Easy Move team. The selected carrier will contact the customer upon its arrival at the pick-up address. On a rare occasion, due to unforeseen factors related to the selected carrier, pick-up can be performed before or after the scheduled date. If the van/driver of the selected carrier will not show up on the scheduled pick-up date or is not providing the services like help to load/unload, the customer assumes the responsibility of informing Easy Move immediately about this fact, so that Easy Move can check the situation with the carrier and fix the issue as soon as possible. The customer is always able to get information about the transit of the shipment by contacting Easy Move support team, which will check the latest transit updates directly with the carrier. The customer shall be informed about the estimated time of delivery in advance. If the consignee is not available at the delivery address, the driver will wait at the address until the customer can organize the unloading of the shipment, as agreed. The customer is aware that any unnecessary waiting by the driver may result in additional costs that shall be borne by the customer. Cancellation and Refund When the customer places the order, at Easy Move we start the preparation for the transport and make a commitment with the carrier that will carry out the transport, which in turn reserves a van and a driver for the transport. Any cancellation of this commitment incurs costs for the carrier and automatically transfers these costs to Easy Move, so the customer can cancel but the amount of the refund will depend on when the cancellation is made. Cancellation up to 48 hours before the collection date - 10% fee on the amount paid. Cancellation less than 48 hours before collection - 30% fee on the amount paid.\')}} After collection of the cargo, no refund is possible. Help to Load/Unload The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work. About Insurance Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance. Types of vans and measurements The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that the client provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van. Data protection Easy Move is committed to treating all data in accordance with international data protection laws, based on the following principles: - Purpose limitation. - Data minimisation. - Accuracy. - Storage limitation. - Integrity and confidentiality (security) - Accountability. Any doubts or requests for data deletion can be requested from the Easy Move team at any time.Lawfulness, fairness and transparency. For any question, please contact us: info@easymoveeurope.com For your company or for a private move, the dedicated van service is the ideal solution. Useful Links Home How it works About US Blogs Contact us Terms and Conditions Contact us Strada Feleacu 3, 077190 Bucharest, Romania Phone: +40 317 801 214 Email : info@easymoveeurope.com  Copyright Easy Move Europe. All Rights Reserved', 'Como funciona Contato Sobre ns Minha conta Abrir conta Entrar Ingls Deutsch Italiano Francs Espaol Portugal Polons Romeno Privacidade e Condies Termos e Condies Nossos termos e condies no se destinam a ocultar informaes ou tirar vantagem de qualquer situao. Nosso nico objetivo  ser justo com todas as partes envolvidas. Em primeiro lugar com o cliente que est pagando para que um servio de qualidade seja feito, em segundo lugar, sermos justos com nossos parceiros, transportadores e motoristas que tm o transporte como meio de subsistncia e com nossa equipe que visa lucrar, mas sem prejudicar ningum, muito pelo contrrio. Condies gerais Ao reservar o servio de entrega em carrinha, o cliente concorda que o envio esteja disponvel, devidamente embalado e seguro para transporte na morada de recolha para que o transportador o recolha entre as 8h00 e as 18h00 ou em outro horrio previamente acordado. com a equipe Easy Move. A transportadora selecionada entrar em co