(1408, 'ro', 'Easy Move Europe is an online digital platform that connects companies and private persons to a huge van network, simplifying and making relocation of business and personal assets affordable, through an algorithm that offers prices instantly, with transparency.', 'Easy Move Europe este o platform digital online care conecteaz companii i persoane private la o reea uria de autoutilitare, simplificnd i fcnd accesibil relocarea afacerilor i a bunurilor personale, printr-un algoritm care ofer preuri instantaneu, cu transparen.', '2023-08-25 00:57:55', '2023-08-25 00:57:55'),
