(1466, 'ro', 'For your company or for a private move, the van delivery service is the ideal solution. \"You can move anything in Europe with a van dedicated only for your cargo. For your company or for a private move, the van delivery service is the ideal solution.\" Advantages: Customized pick-up and delivery time- Collection and deliveries on weekends, day and night -Same day collection available for urgent transport Transport of heavy and bulky items -No special packaging is required -Ideal for transporting fragile items', 'Pentru compania dvs. sau pentru o mutare privata, serviciul de livrare duba este solutia ideala. &quot;Puteti muta orice in Europa cu o duba dedicata doar pentru marfa dumneavoastra. Pentru compania dumneavoastra sau pentru o mutare privata, serviciul de livrare duba este solutia ideala.&quot; Avantaje: Timp personalizat de ridicare i livrare- Colectare i livrri n weekend, zi i noapte -Colectare n aceeai zi disponibil pentru transport urgent Transport de articole grele i voluminoase -Nu este nevoie de ambalaje speciale -Ideal pentru transportul articolelor fragile', '2023-08-25 00:57:55', '2023-08-25 00:57:55'),
(1467, 'ro', 'Frequently Asked Questions Frequently Asked Questions Is there any insurance included when I hire the van service? Yes, every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Do you have only these two types of vans and measurements? No, we have other types, models and sizes of vans. The size you see in the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that you provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van. To transport dangerous items we also have the ADR van and to transport perishable items that need controlled temperature, we have the refrigerated vans, which can be hired separately, just contact us via email or phone and we will provide you with a quote. Will the driver always help to load/unload the load? No, please note that the driver\'s main focus is driving and he will help load and/or unload the cargo if this is contracted to at the time you hire the transport. Please note that not all drivers are physically able to help, so you need to let us know in advance so that the ideal driver is chosen. How does the help service work? When you hire the help service, you need to consider that the driver will help to load/unload from the first floor level to the van and vice versa. For cases where loading/unloading is in apartments that do not have an elevator, you need to let us know in advance, as not all drivers are physically able to go up and down stairs. What cant be shipped? Hazardous goods: e.g. firearms, explosives, ammunition, hazardous materials, radioactives. Illegal goods: Drugs, endangered species, other products illegal under EU laws. Livestock: Live stock animals, horses, pets, mice, worms, insects. Money: Currencies, banknotes and coins. Securities: Bonds, stocks, negotiable documents and all types of securities. About custom procedures, when should I be concerned and who should take care of it for me? For transport within the EU, no special documentation is usually required, but when the country of origin or destination is not part of the European Union, the customer always needs to prepare the documentation in advance. Each country has different rules, so you can consult us and we will guide you through this process.In some cases you will be able to prepare the necessary documentation only with our help, but most of the time it is a broker that will carry out this work. How to pack the goods for shipping? With the dedicated van delivery, you do not need to package your shipment in any specific way. The shipper is able to accommodate the goods in the van however they like, packed or not. However, note that in the movement of the van on the highway one item can crash into the other causing damage and no one wants that to happen, so we still recommend protecting your goods for transport to avoid damage.', 'ntrebri frecvente ntrebri frecvente Exist vreo asigurare inclus atunci cnd angajez serviciul de furgonet? Da, fiecare expediere cu livrarea noastr dedicat cu camioneta este acoperit de conveniile CMR i este disponibil i rspundere extins (pentru transporturile comerciale). Valoarea este n prezent de aproximativ 10 euro pe kilogram i se aplic n cazul producerii de furturi, bunuri deteriorate, neglijen grav n transportul internaional i intern. Avei doar aceste dou tipuri de dube i msurtori? Nu, avem alte tipuri, modele i dimensiuni de camionete. Mrimea pe care o vedei n descriere este o medie, mrimile pot varia. Vom ncerca ntotdeauna s meninem capacitatea contractat de dumneavoastr (13 i 19 metri cubi), aa c este important s ne furnizai ct mai multe informaii despre ncrctura dumneavoastr pentru a v putea trimite duba corespunztoare. Pentru transportul articolelor periculoase avem si duba ADR iar pentru transportul articolelor perisabile care au nevoie de temperatura controlata avem autoutilitare frigorifice, care se pot inchiria separat, doar sa ne contactati prin email sau telefonic si va vom oferi o oferta. oferul va ajuta ntotdeauna la ncrcarea/descrcarea ncrcturii? Nu, v rugm s reinei c principalul obiectiv al oferului este conducerea i el va ajuta la ncrcarea i/sau descrcarea mrfii dac acest lucru este contractat n momentul n care nchiriai transportul. V rugm s reinei c nu toi oferii sunt capabili fizic s v ajute, aa c trebuie s ne anunai n prealabil, astfel nct s fie ales oferul ideal. Cum funcioneaz serviciul de ajutor? Atunci cnd angajai serviciul de ajutor, trebuie s avei n vedere c oferul v va ajuta la ncrcarea/descrcarea de la primul etaj pn la dub i invers. Pentru cazurile n care ncrcarea/descrcarea se face n apartamente care nu au lift, trebuie s ne anunai n prealabil, deoarece nu toi oferii sunt capabili fizic s urce i s coboare scrile. Ce nu poate fi expediat? Mrfuri periculoase: de exemplu arme de foc, explozivi, muniii, materiale periculoase, radioactive. Bunuri ilegale: Droguri, specii pe cale de dispariie, alte produse ilegale conform legislaiei UE. Animale: animale, cai, animale de companie, oareci, viermi, insecte. Bani: monede, bancnote i monede. Valori mobiliare: Obligaiuni, aciuni, documente negociabile i toate tipurile de titluri. Despre procedurile personalizate, cnd ar trebui s fiu ngrijorat i cine ar trebui s se ocupe de asta pentru mine? Pentru transportul n interiorul UE, de obicei nu este necesar nicio documentaie special, dar atunci cnd ara de origine sau de destinaie nu face parte din Uniunea European, clientul trebuie ntotdeauna s pregteasc documentaia n avans. Fiecare ar are reguli diferite, aa c ne putei consulta i v vom ndruma prin acest proces. n unele cazuri vei putea pregti documentaia necesar doar cu ajutorul nostru, dar de cele mai multe ori este un broker care va efectua acest lucru. Cum se mpacheteaz mrfurile pentru expediere? Cu livrarea cu camioneta dedicat, nu trebuie s mpachetai transportul n vreun fel anume. Expeditorul poate gzdui mrfurile n camionet oricum dorete, ambalate sau nu. Totui, reinei c n deplasarea autoutilitarei pe autostrad un articol se poate prbui n cellalt provocnd daune i nimeni nu dorete s se ntmple asta, aa c v recomandm totui s v protejai bunurile pentru transport pentru a evita deteriorarea.', '2023-08-25 00:57:55', '2023-08-25 00:57:55'),
