(1597, 'ro', 'Our terms and conditions are not intended to hide information or take advantage of any situation. We only aim to be fair to all parties involved. Firstly with the customer who is paying for a quality service to be done, secondly, be fair with our partners, carriers and drivers who have transportation as a means of livelihood and with our team that aims to make a profit, but without harming anyone, very on the contrary.', 'Termenii i condiiile noastre nu au scopul de a ascunde informaii sau de a profita de orice situaie. Ne propunem doar s fim coreci cu toate prile implicate. n primul rnd cu clientul care pltete pentru un serviciu de calitate, n al doilea rnd, s fii corect cu partenerii notri, transportatorii i oferii notri care au transportul ca mijloc de trai i cu echipa noastr care i propune s fac profit, dar fr a duna nimnui, foarte dimpotriv.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1598, 'ro', 'When booking the Van delivery service, the customer agrees for the shipment to be available,properly packed and secured for transportation at the pick-up address for the carrier to collect it from 8:00 to 18:00 or another hours agreed previous with Easy Move team. The selected carrier will contact the customer upon its arrival at the pick-up address. On a rare occasion, due to unforeseen factors related to the selected carrier, pick-up can be performed before or after the scheduled date. If the van/driver of the selected carrier will not show up on the scheduled pick-up date or is not providing the services like help to load/unload, the customer assumes the responsibility of informing Easy Move immediately about this fact, so that Easy Move can check the situation with the carrier and fix the issue as soon as possible. The customer is always able to get information about the transit of the shipment by contacting Easy Move support team, which will check the latest transit updates directly with the carrier. The customer shall be informed about the estimated time of delivery in advance. If the consignee is not available at the delivery address, the driver will wait at the address until the customer can organize the unloading of the shipment, as agreed. The customer is aware that any unnecessary waiting by the driver may result in additional costs that shall be borne by the customer.', 'La rezervarea serviciului de livrare Van, clientul este de acord ca expedierea s fie disponibil, ambalat corespunztor i asigurat pentru transport la adresa de ridicare pentru ca transportatorul s o ridice ntre orele 8:00 i 18:00 sau alte ore convenite anterior cu Easy. Mutai echipa. Transportatorul selectat va contacta clientul la sosirea acestuia la adresa de preluare. n cazuri rare, din cauza unor factori neprevzui legat de transportatorul selectat, ridicarea poate fi efectuat nainte sau dup data programat. n cazul n care furgoneta/oferul transportatorului selectat nu se va prezenta la data programat de ridicare sau nu furnizeaz servicii precum ajutor la ncrcare/descrcare, clientul i asum responsabilitatea de a informa imediat Easy Move despre acest fapt, astfel nct Easy Move poate verifica situaia cu transportatorul i poate remedia problema ct mai curnd posibil. Clientul poate obine ntotdeauna informaii despre tranzitul expedierii contactnd echipa de asisten Easy Move, care va verifica cele mai recente actualizri de tranzit direct cu transportatorul. Clientul va fi informat n prealabil cu privire la timpul estimat de livrare. n cazul n care destinatarul nu este disponibil la adresa de livrare, oferul va atepta la adres pn cnd clientul poate organiza descrcarea transportului, conform acordului. Clientul este contient de faptul c orice ateptare inutil din partea oferului poate duce la costuri suplimentare care vor fi suportate de client.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1599, 'ro', 'When the customer places the order, at Easy Move we start the preparation for the transport and make a commitment with the carrier that will carry out the transport, which in turn reserves a van and a driver for the transport. Any cancellation of this commitment incurs costs for the carrier and automatically transfers these costs to Easy Move, so the customer can cancel but the amount of the refund will depend on when the cancellation is made. Cancellation up to 48 hours before the collection date - 10% fee on the amount paid. Cancellation less than 48 hours before collection - 30% fee on the amount paid.\')}} After collection of the cargo, no refund is possible.', 'Cnd clientul plaseaz comanda, la Easy Move ncepem pregtirea pentru transport i ne angajm cu transportatorul care va efectua transportul, care la rndul su i rezerv o dub i un ofer pentru transport. Orice anulare a acestui angajament atrage costuri pentru transportator i transfer automat aceste costuri ctre Easy Move, astfel nct clientul poate anula, dar suma rambursrii va depinde de momentul n care se face anularea. Anulare cu pn la 48 de ore nainte de data colectrii - comision de 10% din suma pltit. Anulare cu mai puin de 48 de ore nainte de colectare - comision de 30% din suma pltit.&#39;)}} Dup ridicarea ncrcturii, nu este posibil nicio rambursare.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1600, 'ro', 'The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work.', 'oferul nu este obligat s ajute la ncrcarea sau descrcarea ncrcturii. Dac clientul are nevoie de asisten, aceasta trebuie s fie contractat direct cu Easy Move. Asistena la ncrcare i/sau descrcare va fi asigurat de la parter pn la dub i de la dub pn la parter, pentru articolele cu greutatea nu mai mare de 20 kg. Pe tot parcursul procesului, clientul trebuie s ajute sau s angajeze teri care s ajute fr excepie. Pentru ajutor la ncrcare sau descrcare n/din apartamente, clientul trebuie s anune n prealabil i este supus aprobrii, deoarece nu toi oferii pot depune efort fizic, iar echipa Easy Move trebuie s aleag din timp oferul pentru ca acesta s poat efectua astfel de lucrri. .', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44');
