(1601, 'ro', 'Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance.', 'Fiecare expediere cu livrarea noastr dedicat cu camioneta este acoperit de conveniile CMR i este disponibil i rspundere extins (pentru transporturile comerciale). Valoarea este n prezent de aproximativ 10 euro pe kilogram i se aplic n cazul producerii de furt, bunuri deteriorate, neglijen grav n transportul internaional i intern. V rugm s reinei c orice daune aduse ncrcturii cauzate de neglijen n ambalajul ncrcturii, aa cum se evideniaz prin fotografii sau videoclipuri, este supus pierderii dreptului de a plti asigurarea.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1602, 'ro', 'The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that the client provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van.', 'Mrimea de pe descriere este medie, mrimile pot varia. Vom incerca intotdeauna sa mentinem capacitatea contractata de dumneavoastra (13 si 19 metri cubi), de aceea este important ca clientul sa ne ofere cat mai multe informatii despre marfa dumneavoastra pentru a va putea trimite duba corespunzatoare.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1603, 'ro', 'Easy Move is committed to treating all data in accordance with international data protection laws, based on the following principles: - Purpose limitation. - Data minimisation. - Accuracy. - Storage limitation. - Integrity and confidentiality (security) - Accountability.', 'Easy Move se angajeaz s trateze toate datele n conformitate cu legile internaionale privind protecia datelor, pe baza urmtoarelor principii: - Limitarea scopului. - Minimizarea datelor. - Precizie. - Limitarea stocrii. - Integritate i confidenialitate (securitate) - Responsabilitate.', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1604, 'ro', 'Any doubts or requests for data deletion can be requested from the Easy Move team at any time.Lawfulness, fairness and transparency. For any question, please contact us: info@easymoveeurope.com', 'Orice ndoieli sau solicitri de tergere a datelor pot fi solicitate oricnd echipei Easy Move. Legalitate, corectitudine i transparen. Pentru orice ntrebare, v rugm s ne contactai: info@easymoveeurope.com', '2023-08-25 01:06:44', '2023-08-25 01:06:44'),
(1605, 'ro', 'How it works Contact About US My account Open Account Log In English Deutsch Italian French Espaol Portugal Polish Romanian Privacy and Condition Terms and Conditions Our terms and conditions are not intended to hide information or take advantage of any situation. We only aim to be fair to all parties involved. Firstly with the customer who is paying for a quality service to be done, secondly, be fair with our partners, carriers and drivers who have transportation as a means of livelihood and with our team that aims to make a profit, but without harming anyone, very on the contrary. General terms When booking the Van delivery service, the customer agrees for the shipment to be available,properly packed and secured for transportation at the pick-up address for the carrier to collect it from 8:00 to 18:00 or another hours agreed previous with Easy Move team. The selected carrier will contact the customer upon its arrival at the pick-up address. On a rare occasion, due to unforeseen factors related to the selected carrier, pick-up can be performed before or after the scheduled date. If the van/driver of the selected carrier will not show up on the scheduled pick-up date or is not providing the services like help to load/unload, the customer assumes the responsibility of informing Easy Move immediately about this fact, so that Easy Move can check the situation with the carrier and fix the issue as soon as possible. The customer is always able to get information about the transit of the shipment by contacting Easy Move support team, which will check the latest transit updates directly with the carrier. The customer shall be informed about the estimated time of delivery in advance. If the consignee is not available at the delivery address, the driver will wait at the address until the customer can organize the unloading of the shipment, as agreed. The customer is aware that any unnecessary waiting by the driver may result in additional costs that shall be borne by the customer. Cancellation and Refund When the customer places the order, at Easy Move we start the preparation for the transport and make a commitment with the carrier that will carry out the transport, which in turn reserves a van and a driver for the transport. Any cancellation of this commitment incurs costs for the carrier and automatically transfers these costs to Easy Move, so the customer can cancel but the amount of the refund will depend on when the cancellation is made. Cancellation up to 48 hours before the collection date - 10% fee on the amount paid. Cancellation less than 48 hours before collection - 30% fee on the amount paid.\')}} After collection of the cargo, no refund is possible. Help to Load/Unload The driver is not obliged to help load or unload the load. If the customer needs assistance,it needs to be contracted directly with Easy Move. Loading and/or unloading assistance will be provided from the ground floor to the van and from the van to the ground floor, for items not heavier than 20 kilos. Throughout the process, the customer must help or hire third parties to help without exception. For help loading or unloading in/from apartments, the customer needs to give advance notice and is subject to approval, as not all drivers can make physical effort and the Easy Move team needs to choose the driver in advance so that he can perform such work. About Insurance Every shipment with our dedicated van delivery is covered by CMR conventions and extended liability is also available (for commercial shipments). The value is currently around 10 euros per kilo and apply to occurrence of theft, damaged goods, gross negligence in international and domestic transport. Please note that any damage to the cargo caused by negligence in the packaging of the cargo,as evidenced by photos or videos, is subject to forfeiture of the right to pay the insurance. Types of vans and measurements The size on the description is an average, sizes may vary. We will always try to maintain the capacity contracted by you (13 and 19 cubic meters), so it is important that the client provide us with as much information as possible about your cargo so that we can send you the appropriate van. Data protection Easy Move is committed to treating all data in accordance with international data protection laws, based on the following principles: - Purpose limitation. - Data minimisation. - Accuracy. - Storage limitation. - Integrity and confidentiality (security) - Accountability. Any doubts or requests for data deletion can be requested from the Easy Move team at any time.Lawfulness, fairness and transparency. For any question, please contact us: info@easymoveeurope.com For your company or for a private move, the dedicated van service is the ideal solution. Useful Links Home How it works About US Blogs Contact us Terms and Conditions Contact us Strada Feleacu 3, 077190 Bucharest, Romania Phone: +40 317 801 214 Email : info@easymoveeurope.com  Copyright Easy Move Europe. All Rights Reserved', 'Cum funcioneaz Contact Despre noi Contul meu Deschidei contul Autentificare Englez Deutsch Italian French Espaol Portugal Polish Romn Confidenialitate i condiii Termeni i condiii Termenii i condiiile noastre nu au scopul de a ascunde informaii sau de a profita de orice situaie. Ne propunem doar s fim coreci cu toate prile implicate. n primul rnd cu clientul care pltete pentru un serviciu de calitate, n al doilea rnd, s fii corecti cu partenerii notri, transportatorii i oferii notri care au transportul ca mijloc de trai i cu echipa noastr care i propune s fac profit, dar fr a duna nimnui, foarte dimpotriv. Condiii generale La rezervarea serviciului de livrare Van, clientul este de acord ca transportul s fie disponibil, ambalat corespunztor i securizat pentru transport la adresa de ridicare pentru ca transportatorul s l ridice ntre orele 8:00 i 18:00 sau alte ore convenite anterior cu echipa Easy Move. Transportatorul selectat va contacta clientul la sosirea acestuia la adresa de preluare. n cazuri rare, din cauza unor factori neprevzui legat de transportatorul selectat, ridicarea poate fi efectuat nainte sau dup data programat. n cazul n care furgoneta/oferul transportatorului selectat nu se va prezenta la data programat de ridicare sau nu furnizeaz servicii precum ajutor la ncrcare/descrcare, clientul i asum responsabilitatea de a informa imediat Easy Move despre acest fapt, astfel nct Easy Move poate verifica situaia cu transportatorul i poate remedia problema ct mai curnd posibil. Clientul poate obine ntotdeauna informaii despre tranzitul expedierii contactnd echipa de asisten Easy Move, care va verifica cele mai recente actualizri de tranzit direct cu transportatorul. Clientul va fi informat n prealabil cu privire la timpul estimat de livrare. n cazul n care destinatarul nu este disponibil la adresa de livrare, oferul va atepta la adres pn cnd clientul poate organiza descrcarea transportului, conform acordului. Clientul este contient de faptul c orice ateptare inutil din partea oferului poate duce la costuri suplimentare care vor fi suportate de client. Anulare si Ramburs In momentul in care clientul plaseaza comanda, la Easy Move incepem pregatirea pentru transport si ne angajam cu transportatorul care va efectua transportul, care la randul sau isi rezerva o duba si un sofer pentru transport. Orice anulare a acestui angajament atrage costuri pentru transportator i transfer automat aceste costuri ctre Easy Move, astfel nct clientul poate anula, dar suma rambursrii va depinde de momentul n care se face anularea. Anulare cu pn la 48 de ore nainte de data colectrii - comision de 10% din suma pltit. Anulare cu mai puin de 48 de ore nainte de colectare - comision de 30% din suma pltit.&#39;)}} Dup ridicarea ncrcturii, nu este posibil nicio rambursare. Ajutor la ncrcare/descrcare oferul nu este obligat s ajute la ncrcarea sau descrcarea ncrcturii. Dac clientul are nevoie de asisten, aceasta trebuie s fie contractat direct cu Easy Move. Asistena la ncrcare i/sau descrcare se va asigura de la parter pn la dub i de la dub pn la parter, pentru articolele cu greutatea nu mai mare de 20 kg. Pe tot parcursul procesului, clientul trebuie s ajute sau s angajeze teri care s ajute fr excepie. Pentru ajutor la ncrcare sau descrcare n/din apartamente, clientul trebuie s anune n prealabil i este supus aprobrii, deoarece nu toi oferii pot depune efort fizic, iar echipa Easy Move trebuie s aleag din timp oferul pentru ca acesta s poat efectua astfel de lucrri. . Despre asigurri Fiecare expediere cu livrarea noastr dedicat cu camioneta este acoperit de conveniile CMR i este disponibil i rspundere extins (pentru transporturile comerciale). Valoarea este n prezent de aproximativ 10 euro pe kilogram i se aplic n cazul producerii de furturi, bunuri deteriorate, neglijen grav n transportul internaional i intern. V rugm s reinei c orice daune aduse ncrcturii cauzate de neglijen n ambalajul ncrcturii, aa cum se evideniaz prin fotografii sau videoclipuri, este supus pierderii dreptului de a plti asigurarea. Tipuri de dube i msurtori Mrimea de pe descriere este medie, mrimile pot varia. Vom incerca intotdeauna sa mentinem capacitatea contractata de dumneavoastra (13 si 19 metri cubi), de aceea este important ca clientul sa ne ofere cat mai multe informatii despre marfa dumneavoastra pentru a va putea trimite duba corespunzatoare. Protecia datelor Easy Move se angajeaz s trateze toate datele n conformitate cu legile internaionale privind protecia datelor, pe baza urmtoarelor principii: - Limitarea scopului. - Minimizarea datelor. - Precizie. - Limitarea stocrii. - Integritate i confidenialitate (securitate) - Responsabilitate. Orice ndoieli sau solicitri de tergere a datelor pot fi solicitate oricnd echipei Easy Move. Legalitate, corectitudine i transparen. Pentru orice intrebare, va rugam sa ne contactati: info@easymoveeurope.com Pentru compania dumneavoastra sau pentru o mutare privata, serviciul dedicat de autoutilitare este solutia ideala. Linkuri utile Acas Cum funcioneaz Despre noi Bloguri Contactai-ne Termeni i condiii Contactai-ne Strada Feleacu 3, 077190 Bucureti, Romnia Telefon: +40 317 801 214 Email: info@easymoveeurope.com  Copyright Easy Move Europe. Toate drepturile rezervate', '2023-08-25 01:06:45', '2023-08-25 01:06:45'),
